   110â†’## [0.19.2] - 2021-11-11
   111â†’
   112â†’**Fixed**
   113â†’
   114â†’- In `set_key`, add missing newline character before new entry if necessary. (#361 by
   115â†’  [@bbc2])
   116â†’
   117â†’## [0.19.1] - 2021-08-09
   118â†’
   119â†’**Added**
   120â†’
   121â†’- Add support for Python 3.10. (#359 by [@theskumar])
   122â†’
   123â†’## [0.19.0] - 2021-07-24
   124â†’
   125â†’**Changed**
   126â†’
   127â†’- Require Python 3.5 or a later version.  Python 2 and 3.4 are no longer supported. (#341
   128â†’  by [@bbc2]).
   129â†’
   130â†’**Added**
   131â†’
   132â†’- The `dotenv_path` argument of `set_key` and `unset_key` now has a type of `Union[str,
   133â†’  os.PathLike]` instead of just `os.PathLike` (#347 by [@bbc2]).
   134â†’- The `stream` argument of `load_dotenv` and `dotenv_values` can now be a text stream
   135â†’  (`IO[str]`), which includes values like `io.StringIO("foo")` and `open("file.env",
   136â†’  "r")` (#348 by [@bbc2]).
   137â†’
   138â†’## [0.18.0] - 2021-06-20
   139â†’
   140â†’**Changed**
   141â†’
   142â†’- Raise `ValueError` if `quote_mode` isn't one of `always`, `auto` or `never` in
   143â†’  `set_key` (#330 by [@bbc2]).
   144â†’- When writing a value to a .env file with `set_key` or `dotenv set <key> <value>` (#330
   145â†’  by [@bbc2]):
   146â†’  - Use single quotes instead of double quotes.
   147â†’  - Don't strip surrounding quotes.
   148â†’  - In `auto` mode, don't add quotes if the value is only made of alphanumeric characters
   149â†’    (as determined by `string.isalnum`).
   150â†’
   151â†’## [0.17.1] - 2021-04-29
   152â†’
   153â†’**Fixed**
   154â†’
   155â†’- Fixed tests for build environments relying on `PYTHONPATH` (#318 by [@befeleme]).
   156â†’
   157â†’## [0.17.0] - 2021-04-02
   158â†’
   159â†’**Changed**
   160â†’
   161â†’- Make `dotenv get <key>` only show the value, not `key=value` (#313 by [@bbc2]).
   162â†’
   163â†’**Added**
   164â†’
   165â†’- Add `--override`/`--no-override` option to `dotenv run` (#312 by [@zueve] and [@bbc2]).
   166â†’
   167â†’## [0.16.0] - 2021-03-27
   168â†’
   169â†’**Changed**
   170â†’
   171â†’- The default value of the `encoding` parameter for `load_dotenv` and `dotenv_values` is
   172â†’  now `"utf-8"` instead of `None` (#306 by [@bbc2]).
   173â†’- Fix resolution order in variable expansion with `override=False` (#287 by [@bbc2]).
   174â†’
   175â†’## [0.15.0] - 2020-10-28
   176â†’
   177â†’**Added**
   178â†’
   179â†’- Add `--export` option to `set` to make it prepend the binding with `export` (#270 by
   180â†’  [@jadutter]).
   181â†’
   182â†’**Changed**
   183â†’
   184â†’- Make `set` command create the `.env` file in the current directory if no `.env` file was
   185â†’  found (#270 by [@jadutter]).
   186â†’
   187â†’**Fixed**
   188â†’
   189â†’- Fix potentially empty expanded value for duplicate key (#260 by [@bbc2]).
   190â†’- Fix import error on Python 3.5.0 and 3.5.1 (#267 by [@gongqingkui]).
   191â†’- Fix parsing of unquoted values containing several adjacent space or tab characters
   192â†’  (#277 by [@bbc2], review by [@x-yuri]).
   193â†’
   194â†’## [0.14.0] - 2020-07-03
   195â†’
   196â†’**Changed**
   197â†’
